Text:
"when people feared what they do not understand"  You think that's changed? they always have, perhaps they always will. Human nature has not changed.
Fear of the unknown is a healthy survival strategy for most animals. We are descended from a very long line of organisms that steered clear of what they did not understand.

Im in search for wicca/witch enchants and learnings through the power of God/Goddes not Satan. Dark magic never is and never will be my thing. Today seemly hard to find the power of light but I wont give up looking for something that's not from the knowledge of Satan.
